Package com.tapsterrock.utility

Class Summary
MppDump This is a trivial class used to dump the contents of an MPP file broken down into its interal file and directory structure, with the content of each of the files written out as hex digits, and their ASCII equivalents.
MppMpx This is a trivial utility class used to provide a simple file format conversion tool that can be run from the command line.
